Package: multiCol
Type: Package
Title: Collinearity detection in a multiple linear regression model
Version: 1.0
Date: 2019-03-06
Author: Román Salmerón Gómez <romansg@ugr.es>, Catalina García García <cbgarcia@ugr.es> and José García García <jgarcia@ual.es>
Maintainer: Román Salmerón Gómez <romansg@ugr.es>
Description: The detection of worrying approximate multicollinearity in a multiple linear regression model is a problem 
	addressed in all existing statistical packages. However, we have detected deficits regarding to the incorrect 
	treatment of qualitative independent variables and the role of the intercept of the model. The objective of this 
	package is to correct these deficits. In this package will be available detection and treatment techniques 
	traditionally used as the recently developed
License: GPL (version 2 or later)
URL: http://colldetreat.r-forge.r-project.org/
